About UnderBar

Java 8s missing functional library. Inspired by conversations with Jeff Bay, underscore.js and clojure

Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
Core Foundational functions inspired by Clojure and underscore.js
Dates Convenience functions to make Java 8s data classes more accessible
Stash Java 8s missing STring HaSH.
IO Functional wrappers for Java 8 IO
